summary: As part of our role in helping Congress to oversee its own funds, we performed certain procedures that the Senate Committee on Rules and Administration requested on behalf of the Secretary of the Senate. We independently counted the cash and noncash items (e.g., cashed checks) in the Senate Disbursing Office on September 22, 2025. We make no overall conclusion on the results. There was a...
title: Senate Disbursing Office: Procedures Related to 2025 Cash Count
